description:
Jarritos Fruit Chamoyada
In a blender, mix 1 pound of fruit with one bottle of your favorite flavor of Jarritos.  Pour the mixture in a blender and freeze overnight.  Eat as is or add chamoy and Chile to taste,  Provecho!
